From 13e84b62ac443b4c389b55793a4c2019fa89f469 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Meng Li <Meng.Li@windriver.com>
Date: Fri, 6 Feb 2026 18:07:50 +0800
Subject: [PATCH 16/30] drivers: ufs: constify the third parameter of
 ufs_tegra_pwr_change_notify()

Based on kernel upstream commit 3bcd901e4257("scsi: ufs: Constify
the third pwr_change_notify() argument"), it needs to constify the
third parameter of ufs_tegra_pwr_change_notify().

Upstream-Status: Pending

Signed-off-by: Meng Li <Meng.Li@windriver.com>
---
 drivers/scsi/ufs/ufs-tegra-common.c | 2 +-
 1 file changed, 1 insertion(+), 1 deletion(-)

diff --git a/drivers/scsi/ufs/ufs-tegra-common.c b/drivers/scsi/ufs/ufs-tegra-common.c
index 2cd8f806..ce24832d 100644
--- a/drivers/scsi/ufs/ufs-tegra-common.c
+++ b/drivers/scsi/ufs/ufs-tegra-common.c
@@ -1166,7 +1166,7 @@ static int ufs_tegra_pwr_change_notify(struct ufs_hba *hba,
 #else
 static int ufs_tegra_pwr_change_notify(struct ufs_hba *hba,
 		enum ufs_notify_change_status status,
-		struct ufs_pa_layer_attr *dev_max_params,
+		const struct ufs_pa_layer_attr *dev_max_params,
 		struct ufs_pa_layer_attr *dev_req_params)
 #endif
 {
-- 
2.34.1

